text: It Is Not Evening Yet () is a 1974 Soviet drama movie directed by Nikolai Rozantsev.Биография Инны МакаровойЕЩЁ НЕ ВЕЧЕР (1974) It stars Inna Makarova, Kirill Lavrov, and Rita Gladunko. == Actors == * Inna Makarova as Inna Kovalyova * Kirill Lavrov as Andrey Pavlov * Rita Gladunko as Tamara Shevyakova * Galina Galchenko as Sveta Pavlova * Rimma Markova as Zinaida Voronina * Olga Markina as Aleksandra Zhigalkina * Lyubov Malinovskaya as Polya * Anna Tveleneva as Lyuba (as Anna Tvelenyova) * Larisa Burkova as Valya * Liliya Gurova as Klava Semykina == References == ==Other websites== * Category:Soviet movies Category:1974 movies Category:Soviet drama movies
title: It Is Not Evening Yet
